title.48: Death's Head: The Body In Question (1991) #1
title.90: The Mutant Misadventures of Cloak and Dagger (1988) #15

description.0: The Super-Soldier and the Swank Soldier of Fortune team-up to rescue the slyly seductive Diamondback from the Serpent Society.
description.9: Drax and the Surfer have enough power between them to annihilate small planets, but can they match the awesome force of Thanos when he wields all of the Infinity Stones?
description.11: Doctor Strange teams up with Red Wolf on a quest for…vengeance! Can the good doctor convince his ally that revenge is not the righteous path?
description.15: Matt is coaxed back to reality by strange dreams featuring key figures from his past. Bullseye gets a new gig courtesy of Kingpin.
description.16: Mesmero breaks into the Braddock Lighthouse and employs mind control over most of the team!
description.17: Bruce's mother convinces the conflicting Hulk personalities to merge within her son's mind. Meanwhile, Banner's lying unconscious in a hospital bed- and will remain there unless his alter egos reach an agreement!
description.18: Tony Stark may be the invincible Iron Man, saving the world one day at a time, but he's also got a multi-billion dollar company to run! He's only one man! Can Tony Stark manage to be the hero everyone needs and still run his father's company?
description.20: A four-way urban melee! Thor defends himself against Excalibur!
description.33: What If Sub-Mariner Had Married the Invisible Woman?
description.35: SUBTERRANEAN WARS PART 4. It's Tony Stark vs. the Outcasts! Let's hope the Golden Avenger makes it out in one piece.
description.41: Punisher protects free speech! When a flag-burning protester meets the fury of a rural Iowa town, Castle steps in to ensure the performance artist lives another day!
description.42: Conan is possessed by an evil sorceress, and while not at his fighting peak, must nonetheless fight for his life against a horrific monster.
description.43: Guest-starring Nick Fury of S.H.I.E.L.D.! Daredevil and Fury must take down a pack of genetically ""perfect"" assassins, three of which have escaped on the streets on New York!
description.44: Captain America and Daredevil guest-star! Witness the origin of the Punisher from an entirely different perspective!
description.45: The Super-Apes and the Red Ghost cause trouble for the Power Pack while a race against the clock begins to restore Dr. Power and Alex!
description.46: Abominatrix returns and her boss is trying to nuke the city!
description.48: Looking for the definitive origin of Death’s Head, robot bounty hunter of the far-flung future? We’ve got you covered here!
description.49: Spider-Man, back in action! After discovering the true identity of Doctor Turner, the wall-crawler and Black Cat team up to restore Peter's powers. But Black Cat's caught in the crossfire! Will the villain of this story hold the upper hand?
description.50: After an attack from the Unspeakable One, the Avengers plan a retreat to their home dimension with Ramskov in tow. Plus, the origin of Rage revealed!
description.51: Diamondback recruits Paladin to help her escape the vengeance of her former allies in the Serpent Society.
description.59: The climactic showdown begins! Strange, Clea, Mordo, Umar -- all against the Dread Dormammu!
description.61: Bullseye's change of heart has him on the heroic track! Will this ace marksman find redemption? Kingpin discovers where Matt Murdock's been ""hiding.""
description.62: Kitty discovers that prep school girls are not as well-mannered as she thought, when she is attacked at St. Searle's School for Young Ladies!
description.63: The fight for control over Tony Stark's body continues! Meanwhile, the Mandarin and Chen Hsu plot to use Fin Fang Foom to reshape the world in their image.
description.64: Torment Part 5.  Writer/Artist Todd McFarlane puts his superstar stamp on Spider-Man with this classic story.  The final showdown - can Spider-Man defeat the Lizard?  And if he does, will he have what it takes to survive Calypso?  Find out in the bloody conclusion to Torment!
description.65: Thor has a not-so-friendly run-in with British super hero team, Excalibur!
description.70: Wolverine doesn't relax much, but when he tries to it never seems to work out. Who will emerge from the darkness to ruin this relaxing evening?
description.72: The First Appearance of the Infinity Gauntlet!  Drax the Destroyer and the Silver Surfer partner up to defeat Thanos -- for real this time.  But Thanos wields the might of the Infinity Gauntlet now!
description.75: What If the Avengers Had Fought the Kree-Skrull War Without Rick Jones?
description.80: The powerful Captain Britain, the shape-changing Meggan, the intangible Shadowcat, the swashbuckling Nightcrawler, the mysterious Phoenix, and Lockheed the Dragon.  Forged in the fires of their tragic pasts, they have banded together to fight a modern-day crusade against the forces of evil.  An age-old evil has firmly established itself in another dimension.  But now, realities are crossing and the malevolent power - with the help of some well-known mutants - threatens to gain a foothold on Earth.
description.84: Dr. Garcia is definitely not on Mexican holiday when the Punisher crashes his scene. Turns out, Garcia has killed a man, and Punisher wants to deliver him to the spouse of the deceased. Revenge is a dish best served bloody!
description.85: He's not dead yet! Well, maybe he is. But at least for now, Conan's corpse is reanimated by the black magic of Jorrma! To make matters worse, the dark sorcerer is powerless to prevent the cadaver's possession by evil spirits.
description.87: Doctor Turner's betrayal has led to this- a battle between Scorpion and a depowered Spider-Man! Spidey may be unable to go to bat, but that doesn't mean he's down for the count. Black Cat guest-stars!
description.88: The Avengers continue to fend off radiation attacks from Ramskov. Running out of options, the team decides to transport their new foe to an alternate dimension where magic reigns supreme.
description.89: Diamondback is put on trial by the Serpent Society and the verdict is death!
description.91: She-Hulks heads decades into the past to team-up with the Invaders!
description.97: Strange's only hope lies in UMAR, Dormammu's twin sister! Can he get his mystical power back to thwart the dread Dormammu? And, what is Baron Mordo planning in the shadows?
description.99: After years of controlling his temper, Wolverine flirts with animalistic rage. Will Logan slip into his former berserker self? Thor does battle with the world's first vampire! Scarlet Witch confronts Past-Master in her final act of salvation.

1.text: Peter Parker’s origin story is recounted in this exciting annual issue!  In the first segment, Peter uncovers a plot between Empire State University and corrupt mega-corporation Roxxon. What is the valuable resource Roxxon wishes to possess? In a word…vibranium! Guest-starring the Ghost and Ultron-5!

2.text: The KORVAC QUEST begins here! Guest starring the Guardians of the Galaxy!

4.text: THE KORVAC QUEST PART 2 The quest rages on! And Thor’s along for the ride!

6.text: THE KINGS OF PAIN PART 3 X-Force and the New Warriors combine forces to investigate a strange energy surge on Muir Island. What is the connection to Moira MacTaggert’s son?

7.text: Storm begins to restore powers to her fellow mutants, turning the tides of their battle in their favor. But will it be enough to defeat the menacing Cameron Hodge?

8.text: The Hobgoblin is losing his mind, and it's up to Spider-Man and Ghost Rider to stop his demonic rampage! Will the Webbed Wonder and the Spirit of Vengeance defeat this vile villain?

9.text: Drax and the Surfer have enough power between them to annihilate small planets, but can they match the awesome force of Thanos when he wields all of the Infinity Stones?

10.text: A recap issue on the key players behind the Super Soldier Project, plus a re-telling of Cap’s origin! In ‘Call of Duty’, Captain America and Nick Fury catch up with the murderous Hydra assassins and discover a deadly agenda behind the "Strucker Gambit."

11.text: Doctor Strange teams up with Red Wolf on a quest for…vengeance! Can the good doctor convince his ally that revenge is not the righteous path?

12.text: Apogee of Disaster Part 5.  Lohan the Satellite Monster is no match for Fury with a little help from the Fantastic Four!

14.text: KINGS OF PAIN PART 1 New Mutants vs. New Warriors? The super-powered teams find themselves face-to-face after they discover a shared connection to the Alliance of Evil. Who will stand victorious with so much at stake?

22.text: All the remaining X-Men converge on Chief Magistrate Anderson and Cameron Hodge, with Genosha and every captive mutant on the line!

24.text: The captured X-Men are on trial in Genosha, forced either to voluntarily become mindless mutates or face death at the hands of Cameron Hodge!

25.text: A group of men hurt Logan's friend, and we know he's not too big a fan of that. These thugs don't know what they're dealing with though…until they see Logan stab a knife into his own hand pain-free. Better run.

27.text: The new Ghost Rider makes himself known to the Marvel Universe at large as his battle with Blackout spills over in the Morlock tunnels beneath New York -- and mutant team X-Factor decides to intervene!

28.text: THE KINGS OF PAIN PART 4 Proteus, the son of Moira MacTaggert, loses control over his psychic powers. Deeply disillusioned, and putting both mutant and human in harm’s way, will X-Factor do whatever it takes to end Proteus’ reign of terror? Guest-starring Cable and his New Mutants!

30.text: Hercules and Sersi’s afternoon stroll down Broadway is interrupted by an explosion from down below! Suddenly a large hole has opened up in the pavement and hordes of Lava Men, Tyrannoids, and Moloids are pouring out! Where are these strange creatures running to? Or perhaps the better question…what are they running from?! PLUS appearances from Thor, Iron Man, Captain America, Black Widow and MORE!

31.text: The West Coast Avengers are AMBUSHED by a group of sentry robots! If that wasn't enough, waiting for them on the other side is Ultron-13.

33.text: What If Spider-Man was married to the Black Cat?

34.text: Unbeing threatens to wipe Quasar out of existence! Thankfully, Origin saves the day.

37.text: Namor travels to Germany when he hears of a disturbing movement that may be collecting followers…

38.text: Venom pulls off a breakout at The Vault, meta-human prison home to Marvel’s most murderous! The Avengers and Freedom Force team-up to put these bad guys back behind bars!

39.text: It begins with a reunion between Moon Knight and his ex-merc partner Bo Olisen, and ends with MK, Frenchie and Marlene trapped in the Hate Factory. Introducing the villainy of Chainsaw and more on the grotesque fate of Midnight.

40.text: The Punisher’s first ‘Nam appearance! Sergeant Frank Castle heads to Vietnam to complete a suicide mission taking down an enemy sniper.

46.text: Abominatrix returns and her boss is trying to nuke the city!

52.text: Yondu goes berserk! Plus, feelings between Vance Astro and Aleta emerge.

53.text: The New Warriors are divided when team members pursue personal agendas. Night Thrasher only has eyes for protecting Silhouette from Bengal, while Speedball investigates his mother’s disappearance. Plus, a shocking ending from Punisher that will unite the Warriors in battle!

55.text: Green Hulk vs. Gray Hulk! Who will win out and claim Bruce Banner?

56.text: A rescue team comprising Cable, Gambit, Marvel Girl, Sunspot, and Forge has been dispatched to rescue mutants captured by the Magistrates, but will they be able to free their fellow X-Men before Wipeout negates their powers?

57.text: As the battle against Star Thief  rages on in space, the New Warriors must divide their efforts between fighting with their new enemy alongside the Inhumans, and defeating Mandroids who have now overrun Stane International.

58.text: Apogee of Disaster Part 4.  Fury's adventures in space continue as the deadly Lohan the Satellite Monster stands in his way. Can Reed Richards and the Fantastic Four help Fury defeat Lohan?

59.text: The climactic showdown begins! Strange, Clea, Mordo, Umar -- all against the Dread Dormammu!

64.text: TORMENT CONCLUSION The final showdown is here! Can Spider-Man defeat the Lizard? And if he does, will he have what it takes to take down Calypso? Find out in the bloody conclusion to TORMENT!
TORMENT CONCLUSION The final showdown is here! Can Spider-Man defeat the Lizard? And if he does, will he have what it takes to take down Calypso? Find out in the bloody conclusion to TORMENT!

67.text: The X-Men rescue team has been captured by Cameron Hodge-but Magistrate Havok's memories as an X-Man begin to stir!

69.text: Wolverine and Psylocke infiltrate the citadel disguised as Magistrates, only to find themselves facing off against former X-Man Havok and the monstrous Cameron Hodge!

70.text: Wolverine doesn't relax much, but when he tries to it never seems to work out. Who will emerge from the darkness to ruin this relaxing evening?

72.text: Drax the Destroyer and the Silver Surfer partner up to defeat Thanos -- for real this time.

74.text: The Grim Reaper awakens, now in ZOMBIE form!

75.text: What If Spider-Man had not married Mary Jane Watson?!

76.text: On your marks, get set, GO! The Runner challenges all the speedsters of earth to race. Who will win? Who will lose? Will an unexpected victor take gold?

79.text: The demon spawn Blackout decides to wreak revenge for his recent disfigurement at the hands of Ghost Rider.  But he won't be starting with Danny Ketch... first up are his closest friends.

81.text: BLOODLUST--A band of drunken vigilantes pursues a crazed psychopath across the icy Yukon waste...they're not taking any prisoners. BLOODLUST--A race of mystical creatures descends on the Canadian north...hungry for souls. BLOODLUST--The mutant Wolverine, a clawed berserker lost in an arctic blizzard--out of his mind. BLOODLUST-- A dark descent into animal savagery.

82.text: Guest-starring Namor’s former Young Ally, the original Human Torch! The Headhunter has Namor’s skull on a platter…but what does she intend to do with it?

83.text: The Punisher, Spider-Man, and Moon Knight against the Secret Empire!

86.text: The Guardians battle Malevolence! Plus: the fate of Martinex and the secret of Starhawk!

90.text: Cloak’s powers may be eating him alive. Dagger gets closer than ever to a dangerous gang leader!

91.text: She-Hulk heads decades into the past to team-up with the Invaders!

95.text: The New Mutants have been captured by the Magistrate Pipeline, and have had their powers taken by the Magistrate Wipeout. Will everyone make it through their escape from the citadel alive?

96.text: Apogee of Disaster Part 3.  What is the Marauder?  Is Fury out of his element in the dangerous outer space?

97.text: Strange's only hope lies in UMAR, Dormammu's twin sister! Can he get his mystical power back to thwart the dread Dormammu? And, what is Baron Mordo planning in the shadows?

98.text: The New Warriors are up against their greatest foe as a new enemy with seemingly endless power emerges? Does the team have what it takes to square off against the Star Thief?
